Package: beacon
Type: Package
Title: BEACON: Burst Event Anomaly Clustering and Outlier Notification
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2025-07-22
Authors@R: person("Sangin", "Kim", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "kimsanginn@gmail.com")
Description: BEACON is a fully data-driven pipeline designed to detect unmodeled gravitational wave (GW) transients. By combining sequential autoregressive modeling (seqARIMA) and anomaly clustering, BEACON provides a low-latency and model-agnostic framework for robust burst detection.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppParallel
